Class DenseGraphLargestCliqueFinder

  • java.lang.Object

      • DenseGraphLargestCliqueFinder
  • public class DenseGraphLargestCliqueFinder
extends AbstractLargestCliqueFinder
    This class implements a clique-finding algorithm that proceeds from larger cliques candidates towards smaller. By construction, the very first clique found is guaranteed to be the largest.
    Author:
    Rodion "rodde" Efremov
